{"tid":1327653,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"個天都幫我地？台灣人係香港上空見到嘅奇景 同一張奧修禪卡好似！！","createTime":"2019-07-17T16:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T06:57:59.000Z","uid":109368,"like":82,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"101e51c1a86315e37cd8a31a182cefa9963215b7","tid":1327653,"uid":109368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:20:15.000Z","msg":"先利申 冇宗教信仰 冇深入研究new age/靈修/塔羅<br />\n純粹分享下神奇事 有咩請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴晚我係facebook見到朋友share一個台灣人post:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fw0EGgg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffw0EGgg.png&h=b6c7d83a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8nVhsWm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8nVhsWm.png&h=3d4b1f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得好神奇好靚 就俾我朋友睇下 <br />\n<br />\n佢望咗一陣就覺得<span style=\"font-size: large;\">同一張奧修卡好似</span>（佢有接觸開)<br />\n<br />\n然後就俾我睇卡嘅相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMJZGjB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMJZGjB.png&h=580690fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9HGUOQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9HGUOQ.png&h=c88539c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見到都覺得幾分相似 無論顏色形狀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且同樣係衝破黑暗<br />\n本身個景象已經好神奇 仲要同呢張卡似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己好奇再search吓張卡點解：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S4X7QdU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS4X7QdU.png&h=c5306728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完之後 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勁中 勁中香港呢刻個處境</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「將所有那些偉大的話語和偉大的教導看成你致命的敵人，避開它們，因為你必須去找出你自己的泉源。你不能成為一個跟隨者或一個模仿者，你必須成為一個原始的個人，你必須自己去找出你最內在的核心，不用嚮導，也不用引導的經典」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地今次抗爭同以往最唔同係 真正冇大台！所有嘢我地自己放膽摸索 自己試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">這張卡片上那個人物的形狀好像一支箭，走向一個單一的焦點，他很清楚地知道他要走到那裡，他走得很快，所以他已經變成幾乎是純粹的能量，但是他的強烈不應該被誤以為是癲狂的能量--像那種瘋狂地高速開車的能量</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n反送中嘅抗爭大家目標非常明確 行動力都好高<br />\n行動比以往更加勇武  但絕對唔係癲狂 而係強烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有一些人會覺得被你的「在」所提升或因為你的「在」而變得更清新，另外有些人或許會覺得受到了威脅或是被打擾，但是別人的意見並不重要，現在已經沒有什麼東西能夠把你抓回來。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n的確有人俾大家嘅抗爭感動/喚醒<br />\n但都有人感到受威脅 可能因為係藍絲/害怕改變/不穩定性<br />\n<br />\n不過我地已經係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">unstoppable 勢不可擋</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實以上一張卡只係咁啱朋友覺得似 我就search<br />\n覺得唔似的話當睇下就算～<br />\n<br />\n但總括嚟講 我感覺個天係幫緊我地 <br />\n願所有手足平安！香港人必定贏！！！！<br />\n加油啊大家 堅持落去 齊上齊落！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">「它是一個黑暗的夜晚，但是帶著強烈的探詢之火，你一定會看到日出。」</span></span>"},{"pid":"600dbd04c443f9b1fc8edbd6b08398f5afe7fdaa","tid":1327653,"uid":166405,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:23:26.000Z","msg":"唔知咩黎但都算幫左我地cheer up<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f73cd555d1ccb4ab94e5f4360a72882eaab70bf","tid":1327653,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26df3fdc625d57e13ba5a99480f26502a655484d","tid":1327653,"uid":199911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"冥冥中自有安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d2720e239d8e0e1672f5436a9a539ef40b25e1","tid":1327653,"uid":134323,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:29:38.000Z","msg":"好係好<br />\n<br />\n但唔好瘋狂打飛機，港共政府未認輸<br />\n我地都俾佢捉左好多人，只係互有勝負"},{"pid":"b6a11264fd9d978b9bb5318975d2708412da2443","tid":1327653,"uid":22302,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:30:53.000Z","msg":"打少陣飛機"},{"pid":"1db29310fe8b3b57087cd398486bc3d705c932c2","tid":1327653,"uid":62011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:31:06.000Z","msg":"香港重生"},{"pid":"b26c13c680caefca88d094da35548c7791b02edf","tid":1327653,"uid":67049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"721見 香港人加油！"},{"pid":"0497327c4b87cea805795ec2ffcd28c9b9681b9a","tid":1327653,"uid":76600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:32:33.000Z","msg":"火之騎士<br />\n要用咩攻擊，大家識做喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc5bbc43d48dfa7a296657fc7726ec619a350b6","tid":1327653,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:45:27.000Z","msg":"信香港人 唔信鬼神"},{"pid":"04f0694d888dc1972e91b2102613a73acf7365dc","tid":1327653,"uid":281198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:49:03.000Z","msg":"奧修講既野﹐盡量睇下就算﹐有睇開就知佢好多金句都係果種你點套用都得既說話。"},{"pid":"b4f080651876f1a24616f0c8d9645689630760b4","tid":1327653,"uid":84021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ca9e6c626524fa69808866fc008c1c27f36b70","tid":1327653,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:40:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">We Are Inevitable!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"a2de2116aa7e51e9be462e1970560385d3cf1504","tid":1327653,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:41:26.000Z","msg":"又真係幾似<br />\n好意頭"},{"pid":"37afcf476651940a7386feb9e2bb133783b40999","tid":1327653,"uid":61517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:20:47.000Z","msg":"想睇真啲啲相<br />\n可唔可以share link"},{"pid":"ce120a375f96def8d2ba6ad19f4a819be08b6bdc","tid":1327653,"uid":33336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:35:40.000Z","msg":"唔好打咁多飛機，多爬山健下身"},{"pid":"dc97d10f1a8d2e6d09e0341ce2ff2c97381b5632","tid":1327653,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:39:52.000Z","msg":"又黎我uncle望到風眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3505bebef533582ca0f3c6586322a6ffd5d8cf","tid":1327653,"uid":263993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:47:49.000Z","msg":"相對論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4517c26c9d0f52f12639c4a1b93383850acf5a","tid":1327653,"uid":176079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"inevitable"}]}